      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MISS TWO STEP (1) struggled to get involved last start at this track, but prior to that won by 3 lengths at this track (21.79) beating Explosive Jem in a Grade 5 on February 17. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings two times from three starts. Looks the one to beat on her best form. HARA'S PEST (3) hit the frame last time at this track but just a few starts ago ran slick time when scoring over 407m at Rockhampton in 23.70. Smart winner three back and looks a key chance on that form. GHOST OF WADDELL (2) was a last start winner (21.66) from Box 1 at this track. Has a solid record from this box including two wins and a minor placing. Leading chance again. MOVE LIGHTLY (8) must be included in calculations.",
